What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Pneumonia Therapeutics Market?

Global Pneumonia Therapeutics Market - Industry Overview

The global pneumonia therapeutics market is expected to grow significantly, owing predominantly to the increasing incidence of pneumonia worldwide, with a particularly strong impact in low- and middle-income countries with less solid healthcare infrastructure. Pneumonia continues to be a prominent cause of death among vulnerable groups, particularly children under the age of five, According to WHO Pneumonia killed 740180 children under the age of 5 in 2019, accounting for 14% of all deaths of children under 5 years old, highlighting the urgent need for more effective treatments and preventive measures. Rising antibiotic resistance, particularly against common infections like Streptococcus pneumoniae, is a major driver of demand for innovative medicines such as next-generation antibiotics, improved vaccines, and supportive care methods.

